snippet.title: Dan Cox
snippet.description: I have been creating video tutorials on tools and programming languages associated with narrative games for over six years. I am best known for tutorial videos on Twine, but I also highlight different interactive fiction tools like Ren'Py, Inform, and Ink as well.
